ncome £ million  net income £ million  aum £ billion  number of employees   subsidiaries parmenion capital partners llc website wwwaberdeenassetcom aberdeen asset management plc is an international investment management group managing assets for both institutions and private investors from offices around the world its head office is in aberdeen scotland the company is listed on the london stock exchange and it is a constituent of the ftse  index in march  the company reached an agreement to merge with the edinburghbased investment company standard life contents  history  operations  references  external links historyedit the company was established in  through a management buyout of an investment trust it was then listed on the london stock exchange in  in recent years it has seen significant growth from acquisitions in  it acquired murray johnstone followed by edinburgh fund managers in  parts of deutsche asset management in  and  glasgow investment managers in  goodman property investors in  certain investment businesses of credit suisse asset management in  and certain contracts and assets from rbs asset management in  in november  lloyds banking group sold scottish widows investment partnership swip to aberdeen asset management in a £m deal the deal made aberdeen asset management the second largest listed fund manager in europe after schroders currently managing £bn  in may  the firm agreed to acquire its us counterpart flag capital management for an undisclosed deal that would double the private equity assets under the company’s control the company sponsored the boat race between  and  in  it signed a fouryear sponsorship agreement with the dad vail regatta to be title sponsor until  the event’s th anniversary the agreement has helped to keep the famous college rowing regatta in philadelphia the groups north american headquarters in march  it took over sponsorship of golfs scottish open for the following three years other sponsorships include the cowes week sailing regatta aberdeen brunei senior masters golf tournament edinburgh rugby club professional golfers colin montgomerie and paul lawrie and formula one driver paul di resta in march  aberdeen asset management reached an agreement to merge with standard life in an allshare merger operationsedit an extreme  class sailing catamaran seen racing off egypt point cowes isle of wight the company operates mainly in the united kingdom but has a growing presence worldwide particularly asia oceania and the americas with over  staff across  offices in  countries its headquarters are in the city of aberdeen where group functions including legal group information and human resources are located and has its major investment desks in london philadelphia and singapore referencesedit  a b c d e annual results  aberdeen asset management retrieved  january    a b c aberdeen asset management history aberdeenassetcom retrieved  april    deutsche bank signs agreement with aberdeen asset management press release deutsche bank  july   deutsche bank to accelerate australian asset management growth through alternative and global product focus press release deutsche bank  march   lloyds sells scottish widows investment in £m deal bbc  november   jon hopkins merging aberdeen asset management plc sees strong rebound in firsthalf results boosted by market gains costcutting proactiveinvestorscouk retrieved    aberdeen boosts alternatives muscle with flag capital buy reuters  may  retrieved  march    the xchanging boat race how it began theboatraceorg  april  archived from the original on  may  retrieved  april    aberdeen dad vail regatta – aberdeen sponsorship aberdeen asset management archived from the original on  december  retrieved  december    aberdeen senior masters dead link  edinburgh rugby edinburgh rugby archived from the original on  april  retrieved  april    aberdeen asset management sponsor colin montgomerie scottishgolfviewcom  january  retrieved  april    paul di resta signs aberde