omics equity and bond teams other affiliations robert john matthews is affiliated with aberdeen asset investments ltd youve reached your  free profiles limit this month upgrade to relsci pro today to enjoy unlimited article views and much more start my free trial ➤ still not convinced check out our full listing of features here are you a relsci pro subscriber login to relsci pro  ➤ not a pro subscriber log in here to manage your alerts keep me signed in login  ➤ forgot your password i have read the lexisnexis terms  conditions sign me up  ➤ aberdeen asset management investment options in australia  australia  aberdeen asset management go to website navigation skip to main content group home institutional investors site australia home   utc » change location aberdeen managed fundsaberdeen mfundsfund reportinginvestor resource centrehow to investabout aberdeen asset managementaberdeen leaders limitednz investorsdisclaimercontact usemployment enquiries search   announcement statement regarding the proposed merger of aberdeen asset management plc and standard life plc find out more     total client assets under management and advice au billion source aberdeen asset management plc  march  aberdeen group overview quick links daily fund prices fund performance fund reporting market reports thought leadership forms   contact us fatca compliance     email services receive the latest fund and world market updates directly into your inbox email signup     online services for use by institutional clients advisers and platforms only login required sara web   investment and asset management at aberdeen dedicated to doing one thing well at aberdeen asset management is our sole focus we are a global investment management group managing assets for both institutional and retail clients from offices around the world aberdeen is not distracted by competing internal business interests so we are clearly focused on one purpose managing assets for our clients our approach to achieving performance from our funds is open and straightforward no black boxes no short cuts simply asset management in australia aberdeen manages assets for a range of global and domestic clients including listed investment companies managed investment schemes and segregated mandates our clients access our investment expertise in equities fixed income property and alternatives via segregated and pooled products we invest worldwide and follow a predominantly longonly approach based on fundamentally sound investments   aberdeen mfunds aberdeen funds now on mfund � a new way to access unlisted managed funds via the asx more on mfunds     more diversification less duplication aberdeen ex australian equities fund find out more     we see the big in small at aberdeen we see big opportunities in the small company sector more on the aberdeen australian small companies fund     aberdeen tv at aberdeen tv you can watch the latest aberdeen fund manager interviews portfolio and investment updates and register for live events find out more     for institutional investors we manage funds and segregated portfolios across all asset classes including equities fixed income property and alternative solutions find out more     aberdeen managed funds aberdeens funds offer investors a comprehensive choice of domestic regional global and emerging markets funds�view our funds available in each asset class funds by asset class         accessibility technical support privacy and cookies website feedback back to top  aberdeen asset management privacy and cookies policy the attention of users is drawn to aberdeen’s privacy and cookies policy which includes details on the use of performance identification and targeting cookies both our own and third parties to enhance the functionality of the website to enable the group to monitor usage and to assist with future communications by continuing to use this site users will be deemed to have accepted this policy and the use of cookies for these limited purposes 